            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"資金撤離加速 阿瑞斯和阿波羅限制私募信貸基金贖回\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JuIvV2tABgT0lDTaDK33LQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/3ad4ff20-27d9-11f1-a6f6-c9dd6a527adb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">資金撤離加速 阿瑞斯和阿波羅限制私募信貸基金贖回</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
